{"sequence":37,"timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:51:00.019384501Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-df55f35e","body":"finding_summary: `execute_iterative_plan_and_implement_stage` appends `implementer_iteration_completed` before it durably advances `active_run.iterative_implementer_state`, while `resume_iteration_counters` restores loop progress only from the interrupted snapshot. If the `run.json` write fails, or the process dies after the journal append succeeds, resuming the run will replay an already-completed implementer iteration and can duplicate code edits / journal entries.\naffected_files:\n- src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:6211-6249\n- src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:1113-1125\nremediation_hint: Reconstruct iterative loop progress from `ImplementerIterationCompleted` journal events on resume, or otherwise make the journal/snapshot update ordering crash-safe so a completed iteration cannot be replayed.","dedup_key":"1f5c0930db05023223ef1b16cb662d2190a1a080d9af226cc4de863ee1f436d3","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260418021911","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":38,"timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:51:00.029063403Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-38752dd9","body":"finding_summary: The custom diff fingerprint hashes file paths, sizes, contents, and symlink targets, but it never includes regular-file mode bits. In the filesystem fallback and in the untracked-file branch, a chmod-only change (for example, making a newly created script executable) produces the same fingerprint, so the loop can treat a real workspace change as 'stable' and exit early.\naffected_files:\n- src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:5894-5913\n- src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:5972-5988\nremediation_hint: Include permission/mode bits in the fallback and untracked-file hashes, or switch to a status representation that preserves executable-bit changes for those paths.","dedup_key":"8d9dbba53ea1ca1f50949b435e2e59c1e008afe3d0ff5c55751f46bd2c265d93","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260418021911","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
